==教育==
伊斯蘭國攻佔摩蘇爾後，該市的學校採取男女隔離的方式授課。該城市最大的大學[[摩蘇爾大學|摩蘇爾大學]]于2014年被伊斯蘭國關閉，及後於2017年伊拉克軍隊從伊斯蘭國手中奪回控制權後重開。<ref>{{cite news|title=ISIS Takeover In Iraq: Mosul University Students, Faculty Uncertain About The Future Of Higher Education|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/isis-takeover-iraq-mosul-university-students-faculty-uncertain-about-future-higher-1731468|publisher=IBT|date=3 December 2014|accessdate=2015-03-06|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924122929/http://www.ibtimes.com/isis-takeover-iraq-mosul-university-students-faculty-uncertain-about-future-higher-1731468|dead-url=no}}</ref>

